Package com.epoch.translations

Classes that handle translations into other languages.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PhraseTransln
    Holds the translations of hardwired ACE phrases into a single language.
    QSetAllTranslns
    Utility class containing static methods for writing or retrieving all of the translations of a question set header, or for retrieving all of the translations of a single question's statement, question data, and evaluators.
    QSetTransln
    Holds the translation of all of the questions in a master-authored question set into a single language.
    QTranslns
    Stores all of the translations of the components of a question.
    TranslnsMap
    Stores a map of a phrase's translations, keyed by languages.
